components.name: Initialize Pipeline
components.description: Marks the start of the Dataform transformation pipeline; acts as a placeholder entry point.

upstream_policy.description: No upstream dependencies; this is the first node.

components.name: Parse Input Parameters
components.description: Extracts and formats DAG run configuration and logical date into a compilation configuration object passed via XCom.

components.name: Create Dataform Compilation Result
components.description: Calls the Google Cloud Dataform API to create a compilation result using the parsed parameters; returns the result name for workflow invocation.

upstream_policy.description: Executes after parameters have been parsed.

components.name: Create Dataform Workflow Invocation
components.description: Triggers a Dataform workflow execution using the previously created compilation result; returns an invocation ID for monitoring.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after a compilation result has been created.

components.name: Monitor Workflow Invocation State
components.description: Polls the Dataform workflow invocation until it reaches a terminal state (SUCCEEDED or FAILED).

upstream_policy.description: Executes after the workflow invocation has been created.

components.name: Finalize Pipeline
components.description: Marks successful completion of the pipeline after the workflow sensor finishes.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after the workflow state sensor reports completion.
